title: SPY+ Presents: Country Livin' w/ John John Florence + The Murena
description: The SPY+ crew recently spent some quality hours on Oahu with John Florence. He went on to win the 2011 Volcom Pipe Pro, but not before we got him on camera at his favorite local spots in the water and on land, from Backdoor, Pipe and Ehukai to Banzai Skatepark and Ted's Bakery... Country livin' is good for John.
